cast.overview: When an attack on the Kingsman headquarters takes place and a new villain rises, Eggsy and Merlin are forced to work together with the American agency known as the Statesman to save the world.
cast.title: Kingsman: The Golden Circle

details.biography: Kaye Brown in an English actress and dancer, originally from the West Indies and later moving to England. She trained at Crewe & Alsager College of Higher Education and London Contemporary Dance School, graduating with a BA (Hons) in Drama and Dance. Her other television credits include roles in Great Performances, Ted Lasso, Close to Me, Casualty, Vera and Doctors. Film roles include Kingsman: The Golden Circle, Finding Your Feet, Jingle Jangle: A Christmas Story, SeaView and A Christmas Number One.
details.name: Kaye Brown
